<h3>
CfP: 14th International Pragmatics Conference (IPRA): “Adaptability”
</h3>
</div>
<div class='well'>
<p class=''>
<b>
Ort:
</b>
Antwerpen, Belgien
</p>
<p class=''>
<b>
Frist:
</b>
2014-09-15
</p>
<p class=''>
<b>
